n \in \mathbb{N}, x \in \mathbb{R}
\cos(nx)=\sum_{j=0}^{[n/2]} (-1)^j {n \choose 2j} (\cos x)^{n-2j} (\sin x)^{2j}
\sin(nx)=\sum_{j=0}^{[(n-1)/2]} (-1)^j {n \choose 2j+1} (\cos x)^{n-2j-1} (\sin x)^{2j+1}
n\in\mathbb{N}
x\in\mathbb{R}
k\in\{0,1,\dots,n\}
k=2j
0 \leq j \leq [\frac{n}{2}]
k=2j+1
0 \leq j \leq [\frac{n-1}{2}]
 \cos(nx)+i\sin(nx) =e^{inx} =(\cos x+i\sin x)^n =\sum_{k=0}^{n}i^k\binom{n}{k}\cos^{n-k}x\sin^{k}x 
